	</span>
</h3>
<p>TTS models are used to create voice assistants on smart devices. These m=
odels are a better alternative compared to concatenative methods where the =
assistant is built by recording sounds and mapping them, since the outputs =
in TTS models contain elements in natural speech such as emphasis.</p>
